<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-11128] implicit-this access within closure to private members in declaring class when invoked from derived class</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-11128</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Separate ticket for implicit-this style access to private fields, methods, and properties from closure within declaring class.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Consider the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;C {
    protected &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; protectedMethod() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; closure = { -&amp;gt;
            privateMethod()
        }
        closure()
    }
    private &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; privateMethod() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;hello world&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
    }
}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;D &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; C {
    void test() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; result = protectedMethod()
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; result == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;hello world&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
    }
}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; D().test()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See also &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2433&quot; title=&quot;Closure in base class unable to call private methods when invoked from derived class&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-2433&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-2433&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2565&quot; title=&quot;Exception with inheritance and private method calls from a closure&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-2565&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-2565&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3073&quot; title=&quot;Private inheritance bug: Closure accessing private method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-3073&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-3073&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3142&quot; title=&quot;Unable to access inherited private fields from a closure within an inherited method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-3142&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-3142&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4083&quot; title=&quot;private members should be accessible in closures used from sub classes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-4083&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-4083&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4084&quot; title=&quot;Private class property not visible from closure in a super. invoked method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-4084&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-4084&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4692&quot; title=&quot;Regression calling private fields from a Closure when subclassed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-4692&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-4692&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5438&quot; title=&quot;Private field inaccessible in closure when using a subclass&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-5438&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-5438&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6335&quot; title=&quot;MissingPropertyException when private static property is used inside a nested closure and called from a child class&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-6335&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-6335&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-8905&quot; title=&quot;MissingMethodException when private method is called on parent class in a closure&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-8905&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-8905&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-9987&quot; title=&quot;MissingMethodException when a base class calls a private static method inside a closure &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-9987&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-9987&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-10723&quot; title=&quot;Closure in parent class can&amp;#39;t access private method in same class when called from a child class&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-10723&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-10723&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, et al.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
